# holdersComma

- _holdersComma(n)_

Answer Holders, also called Holdrians, comma raised to the number _n_.
It is the irrational number equal to one step of the 53-EDO tuning.

```
>>> 1.holdersComma
2.nthRoot(53)

>>> 1.holdersComma
1.0132

>>> 1.holdersComma
>>> .ratioToCents
22.6415

>>> 1.holdersComma
>>> .ratioToSavarts
5.6798

>>> 53.holdersComma
2
```

